# Kemere lab behavioral recordings

Behavioral video and image recordings organized under the BIDS `beh` datatype following BEP047 (audio/video/image recordings).

Generated from `sourcedata/raw` by `code/convert_raw_to_bids.py`.

- `_video` / `_audiovideo`: overhead behavioral recordings (MP4).
- `_image`: still frames / average frames (PNG).
- The `recording-<camera>` entity identifies the camera view.
- Lab tracking / conversion parameters from the source `*.settings` files are preserved in each media sidecar under `TrackingSettings`.

Media metadata was extracted with FFmpeg's `ffprobe`.
